and we give back,

00:19:11.790 --> 00:19:14.010
which we think is
very important,

00:19:14.010 --> 00:19:15.390
and something that
we'll continue

00:19:15.390 --> 00:19:19.470
to do for at least
the rest of my life.

00:19:19.470 --> 00:19:25.680
We believe that having a very
diverse company is important.

00:19:25.680 --> 00:19:28.440
We have people from
all walks of life.

00:19:28.440 --> 00:19:35.220
We have people from
the Chinese factory

00:19:35.220 --> 00:19:39.900
sewing machine operators
to top-level executives.

00:19:39.900 --> 00:19:42.265
And I'm sure many
of you are thinking

00:19:42.265 --> 00:19:44.220
of what to do in the future.

00:19:44.220 --> 00:19:49.230
This business offers so
much amazing opportunity.

00:19:49.230 --> 00:19:51.550
If you just look
at the marketing

00:19:51.550 --> 00:19:55.690
area and the social networking,
which we're very involved with,

00:19:55.690 --> 00:19:57.880
that spells opportunity.

00:19:57.880 --> 00:19:59.740
If you look at
the manufacturing,

00:19:59.740 --> 00:20:02.050
that's all about opportunity.

00:20:02.050 --> 00:20:06.280
And you look at the leadership
in the executive programs

00:20:06.280 --> 00:20:10.930
Macy's and companies like ours
offer, it's really incredible,

00:20:10.930 --> 00:20:12.320
and the sky is the limit.

00:20:12.320 --> 00:20:16.000
So if you're contemplating
being in this business

00:20:16.000 --> 00:20:18.760
at some point in time,
the opportunities

00:20:18.760 --> 00:20:23.410
are endless, not to mention
the creative area, which

00:20:23.410 --> 00:20:26.420
is probably my favorite.

00:20:26.420 --> 00:20:31.660
It is, I would say, a
dream come true to be

00:20:31.660 --> 00:20:35.530
able to sit with a design
team, sit with creative people

00:20:35.530 --> 00:20:39.560
and come up with new
ideas, execute those ideas,

00:20:39.560 --> 00:20:41.650
put them into the
stores, and actually see

00:20:41.650 --> 00:20:45.250
people wearing the ideas
or wearing the clothes

00:20:45.250 --> 00:20:47.320
or wearing the accessories
on the streets.

00:20:47.320 --> 00:20:48.850
There's nothing
better than that.

00:20:48.850 --> 00:20:51.670
That's a fulfilling feeling.

00:20:51.670 --> 00:20:54.430
And I would only
wish some of you

00:20:54.430 --> 00:20:58.190
could experience
that in your lives.

00:20:58.190 --> 00:21:01.100
In addition to, I
think, the success

00:21:01.100 --> 00:21:06.350
we've had in building a brand
and building a product line,

00:21:06.350 --> 00:21:09.680
I would say that it all
revolves around the people

00:21:09.680 --> 00:21:11.450
and the quality of the people.

00:21:11.450 --> 00:21:13.790
I have an all-star team.

00:21:13.790 --> 00:21:17.720
