00:21:31.250 --> 00:21:33.140
It is really all about a team.

00:21:33.140 --> 00:21:34.700
It's not about me.

00:21:34.700 --> 00:21:36.980
It is not about Fred
Gehring, the CEO.

00:21:36.980 --> 00:21:38.640
But it's about a team.

00:21:38.640 --> 00:21:41.660
