we have subteams.

00:21:41.660 --> 00:21:43.040
We have our marketing team.

00:21:43.040 --> 00:21:44.120
We have our design team.

00:21:44.120 --> 00:21:45.950
We have our production team.

00:21:45.950 --> 00:21:47.600
We have our accessory team.

00:21:47.600 --> 00:21:51.020
We have a team just searching
the world for new fabrics.

00:21:51.020 --> 00:21:52.820
We have a team just
going out, looking

00:21:52.820 --> 00:21:55.130
for buttons in the world.

00:21:55.130 --> 00:21:58.670
We have teams on the
ground just doing events.

00:21:58.670 --> 00:22:02.240
And we have teams just
working on fashion collections

00:22:02.240 --> 00:22:03.350
for the runway.

00:22:03.350 --> 00:22:06.170
